      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $n,p \\in \\N^*$ avec $n \\ge p$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n,p \\in \\N^*\\)</span> avec <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n \\ge p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "52476c1c-1ba0-452d-a294-12c12d6ce81b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "V{\\'e}rifier que $C_n^kC_k^p = C_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}$ pour $p \\le k \\le n$.",
        "html": "<p>V<span>é</span>rifier que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(C_n^kC_k^p =\nC_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}\\)</span> pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p \\le k \\le\nn\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bc88df41-22c8-48c8-885f-4e00a692a8a7",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{k=0}^n \\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n\n\\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c0fa2c5b-eded-4956-8cf8-cb729c38b0cf",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire $\\sum_{k=0}^n (-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0$ si $p < n$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n\n(-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt;\nn\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "31484e99-768e-476d-b098-d1781d818cd9",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$0$ si $p < n$, $(-1)^n$ si $p = n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span> si <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt; n\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((-1)^n\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p =\nn\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
